title: Let's get Fitzmagic, plus more SuperFriend Week 4 takeaways (Football 8/30)
description:
Description: The next NFL game you see will be a regular season one, so Will Brinson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest news and notes from the NFL Week 4 preseason, including the rise of Ryan Fitzpatrick (8:00), the Bengals struggles (15:00), Daniel Jones performance (18:00), the Patriots wide receivers (23:00), Kyler Murray vs. Dwayne Haskins (29:00) and their list of teams they're up versus down on after four weeks of the preseason.
